scene.message:
Ayase: What? You're so slow.{nl}
If there's nothing,{nl}
I'm leaving!{waitkey}Later.{waitkey}{ret}

Toro: W-wait!{nl}
I'll say it, I'll say it,{nl}
I'll say it!{waitkey}...Okay?{waitkey}{ret}

Toro: I love youuuu!{waitkey}I{wait_fr:64} love you soooo much!!{waitkey}{clearbox}P-please please please{nl}
go go go out with me!!{waitkey}{clearbox}I'll d-d-definitely{nl}
make you happly{wait_fr:18} hoppy{wait_fr:18} happy{wait_fr:18}, I will!{waitkey}{clearbox}Huff huff, wheeze wheeze...{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: ...{wait_fr:18}...{wait_fr:18}...{wait_fr:18}...{wait_fr:18}...{wait_fr:18}...{wait_fr:18}...{wait_fr:18}{nl}
Say that after you look{nl}
in a mirror.{waitkey}You're a hard pass.{waitkey}{clearbox}Anyway, Ayase's outta here.{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: You're fat and slow,{nl}
you just grin no matter{nl}
what's said to you,{waitkey}{clearbox}always in the same shirt,{nl}
only ever sleeping, reading{nl}
manga, or eating - what's{waitkey}even fun about that?{waitkey}{clearbox}Everything about you's a no!{nl}
Ayase doesn't get it.{waitkey}{ret}

Toro: Th-that's cruel......{waitkey}Then what's fun for{nl}
you, Ayase?{waitkey}{clearbox}Laughing when you're not{nl}
happy, going along with the{nl}
crowd even when it's dumb...{waitkey}Are you scared of{nl}
being alone?{waitkey}{ret}
